column4:
Elijah Cummings was a friend, a mentor, and a leader with steadfast moral clarity. I am heartbroken.

@RepCummings served this nation until his very last day — I’ve been honored to learn from him as his Vice Chair. My thoughts are with his family.

Our country has lost a great.

@McKenziePark8 @AltmireRobert Hey! Here’s a list of cosponsors of #MedicareForAll in the House.

I’m one of them.👇
https://t.co/FgWmczAu2P

I wanted to check in with you all on #WorldSuicidePreventionDay.

Suicide has touched my life in many ways — if you are struggling, you are not alone. Please reach out.

24/7 Resources 👇
@800273TALK: 1-800-273-8255
@TrevorProject LGBTQ Hotline: 1-866-488-7386 https://t.co/Y6MppU9iGF

You’re not safe in school, you’re not safe in church, you’re not safe shopping with your kids on the weekends.

@senatemajldr, what’s it going to take for you to act? How many grieving families? How many traumatized kids?

Today, my heart is with #ElPaso. 🧡
